original: Fredin, Nils Gustaf Kristoffer, tandläkare, Västervik, f. 22/4/95 i Sthlm av bruksäg. Nils F. o. Emma Gull-berg. G. 27 m. Runa Anna Margareta Lindberg. Barn: Göran Nils Folke f. 35. — Studiex. i Sthlm, Chirurg. dent. i Strasbourg 31, tandil. 37. Prakt, i Smål. Rydaholm samt skoltandl. i Ry-daholms s:n 38, prakt, i Västervik sed. 38.
translated: Fredin, Nils Gustaf Kristoffer, dentist, Västervik, born on April 22, 1895 in Stockholm to mill owner Nils F. and Emma Gullberg. Married on 1927 to Runa Anna Margareta Lindberg. Children: Göran Nils Folke born in 1935. He graduated from high school in Stockholm and received his Chirurg. dent. degree in Strasbourg in 1931. He became a practicing dentist in Rydaholm in Småland county and a school dentist in Rydaholm parish in 1938. He started practicing dentistry in Västervik in 1938.
